      • threeLettersCode

        public static String threeLettersCode(HashMap<String,String> h,
                                      String s)
        Parameters:
        h - a map mapping language name to language code that complements ISO639_3; h is defined in eng/EnglishLangToCode.java
        s - the language name (e.g., "Afrikaans")
        Returns:
        the three letter language code, if available (e.g., "afr") otherwise returns the two letter language code, if available (e.g., "af"), otherwise returns the input language name s and prints a warning
